    <text x="970" y="350" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#dc2626"></text>
    <line x1="970" y1="362" x2="970" y2="400" stroke="#7c3aed" stroke-width="2"/>
    <rect x="910" y="400" width="120" height="20" rx="5" fill="#faf5ff" stroke="#7c3aed"/>
    <text x="970" y="415" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#7c3aed" font-weight="700">DS18B20 DQ</text>
  </g>

  <!-- Power rails downward from DPC3512 -->
  <line x1="190" y1="240" x2="190" y2="300" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="2.5" marker-end="url(#pa)"/>
  <line x1="450" y1="240" x2="450" y2="300" stroke="#eab308" stroke-width="2.5" marker-end="url(#pb)"/>
  <line x1="710" y1="240" x2="710" y2="300" stroke="#16a34a" stroke-width="2.5" marker-end="url(#pc)"/>
  <line x1="970" y1="240" x2="970" y2="300" stroke="#7c3aed" stroke-width="2.5" marker-end="url(#pd)"/>

  <!-- GND note -->
  <rect x="200" y="460" width="800" height="60" rx="8" fill="#f1f5f9" stroke="#94a3b8" stroke-width="1"/>
  <text x="600" y="486" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" font-weight="700" fill="#475569">GND 共地说明</text>
  <text x="600" y="508" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#64748b">DPC3512 四路输出的 GND 在电源端已连通 → 所有模块 GND 接到任意一路 GND 即可共地</text>

  <!-- Warning -->
  <rect x="200" y="540" width="800" height="40" rx="8" fill="#fef2f2" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="1.5"/>
  <text x="600" y="565" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#dc2626" font-weight="700">DS18B20 使用 ESP32 板载 3.3V 供电, DQ 经 4.7kΩ 上拉至 3.3VESP32 由 CH1 (5V→USB-C→板载LDO→3.3V) 供电</text>
</svg>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>3.2 电流预算</h3>
<div class="tbl-wrap">
<table>
<thead><tr><th>电源通道</th><th>电压</th><th>额定</th><th>负载</th><th>估算电流</th><th>余量</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>CH1</td><td>5V</td><td>3A</td><td>ESP32-S3 (含LCD背光+触摸)</td><td>~1.5A</td><td style="color:#10b981;">50%</td></tr>
<tr><td>CH2</td><td>12V</td><td>2A</td><td>48F704P840 电机</td><td>~1.2A (满载)</td><td style="color:#10b981;">40%</td></tr>
<tr><td>CH3</td><td>5V</td><td>2A</td><td>LCD屏 + Y01 + PAM8302 + WS2812</td><td>~0.8A</td><td style="color:#10b981;">60%</td></tr>
<tr><td>CH4</td><td>3.3V</td><td>1A</td><td>DS18B20 1-Wire (~1mA)</td><td>&lt;10mA</td><td style="color:#10b981;">99%</td></tr>
<tr class="total-row"><td colspan="4">AC 220V 端总功率估算</td><td colspan="2">~35W (含开关电源损耗)</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<h2>四、分步接线指南</h2>

<div class="card">
<h3>步骤 1: LCD 屏幕 (TK043F1509)</h3>
<div class="steps">
<div class="step"><div class="num">1</div><div class="info"><strong>确认排线方向</strong><span>TK043F1509 使用 40pin FPC 排线 (0.5mm间距), 确认引脚1位置 (通常有三角标记)</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">2</div><div class="info"><strong>连接8位数据总线 (D0-D7)</strong><span>GPIO4→D0, GPIO5→D1, GPIO6→D2, GPIO7→D3, GPIO15→D4, GPIO16→D5, GPIO17→D6, GPIO18→D7。8条杜邦线逐一连接, 建议用不同颜色区分</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">3</div><div class="info"><strong>连接控制线</strong><span>GPIO1→CS, GPIO42→RS(D/C), GPIO2→WR(PCLK), GPIO46→RST, GPIO19→BL(背光PWM)</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">4</div><div class="info"><strong>连接触摸I2C</strong><span>GPIO20→SDA, GPIO13→SCL。每条线需焊接4.7kΩ上拉电阻至3.3V (ESP32板载3.3V引脚)</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">5</div><div class="info"><strong>供电</strong><span>LCD VCC(pin2)→CH3 5V, GND(pin1)→GND。同时将100nF退耦电容并联在VCC和GND之间</span></div></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>步骤 2: 电机接线 (48F704P840)</h3>
<div class="steps">
<div class="step"><div class="num">1</div><div class="info"><strong>供电接线 (先断电!)</strong><span>红线→CH2 12V(+), 黑线→GND(-)。将470µF/25V电解电容并联在12V和GND之间 (长脚→12V, 短脚→GND)，100nF陶瓷电容也并联上</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">2</div><div class="info"><strong>控制信号</strong><span>黄线(START)→GPIO21 (GPIO21已焊4.7kΩ下拉至GND确保默认停机), 绿线(PWM)→GPIO39, 蓝线(FG)→GPIO40 (GPIO40需上拉3.3V)</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">3</div><div class="info"><strong>验证</strong><span>上电后电机不转 (START默认低电平)。通过串口或MQTT发送启动命令后GPIO21拉高, 电机启动, GPIO39输出25kHz PWM调速</span></div></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>步骤 3: 传感器接线</h3>
<div class="steps">
<div class="step"><div class="num">1</div><div class="info"><strong>Y01 空气质量传感器</strong><span>VCC→CH3 5V, GND→GND, TX→GPIO9(ESP32 RX), RX→GPIO41(ESP32 TX)。注意TX↔RX交叉连接! 加100nF退耦电容</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">2</div><div class="info"><strong>DS18B20 温度传感器 (1-Wire 三线制)</strong><span>DQ→GPIO8 + 4.7kΩ上拉至3.3V (必须!), VDD→3.3V, GND→GND。数字传感器, 12-bit分辨率, 0.0625°C精度, 出厂已校准。CRC-8校验确保数据完整性</span></div></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>步骤 4: 音频接线</h3>
<div class="steps">
<div class="step"><div class="num">1</div><div class="info"><strong>RC低通滤波</strong><span>GPIO48 → 100Ω电阻 → (10nF电容→GND) → PAM8302 IN+。滤波截止频率 fc = 1/(2π×100Ω×10nF) ≈ 159kHz</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">2</div><div class="info"><strong>PAM8302 功放</strong><span>VCC→CH3 5V, GND→GND, IN-→GND, SD→3.3V(使能)。OUT+→喇叭+, OUT-→喇叭-</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">3</div><div class="info"><strong>验证</strong><span>开机应听到开机提示音 (如果有)。按键应有按键音反馈。报警时应有报警音</span></div></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>步骤 5: WS2812 状态灯接线</h3>
<div class="steps">
<div class="step"><div class="num">1</div><div class="info"><strong>连接</strong><span>WS2812 DIN→GPIO38 (RMT驱动, GRB字节顺序), VCC→CH3 5V, GND→GND。GPIO38输出3.3V电平, WS2812可接受3.3V逻辑信号</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">2</div><div class="info"><strong>灯光优先级</strong><span>红色闪烁(报警) > 橙/红色(关机中) > 蓝色闪烁(WiFi连接失败) > 黄色闪烁(WiFi连接中) > 自定义颜色/正常模式</span></div></div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
