<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<h2>六、I2C 触摸总线 &amp; 上拉电阻详解</h2>

<div class="card">
<h3>6.1 电路原理</h3>
<p>FT5x06 触摸控制器通过 I2C1 总线与 ESP32-S3 通信。I2C 的 SDA 和 SCL 是开漏(Open-Drain)输出, 必须通过上拉电阻拉到高电平才能正常工作。</p>
<div class="wire-box">
<pre style="font-family:Consolas,monospace;font-size:.85em;line-height:1.6;">
    ESP32 3.3V
       │
    ┌──┴──┐
    │     │
    R1    R2    R1 = R2 = 4.7kΩ ±5%
   4.7k   4.7k
    │     │
    ├─────┴──── GPIO20 (SDA) ──── FT5x06 SDA
    │
    └────────── GPIO13 (SCL) ──── FT5x06 SCL
</pre>
</div>
<div class="callout info">
  <strong>为什么需要上拉?</strong>
  I2C设备只能将总线拉低, 不能主动拉高。上拉电阻在空闲时将总线恢复到高电平 (逻辑1)。无上拉时总线永远低电平, 通信失败。
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>6.2 焊接方式</h3>
<p>将4.7kΩ电阻 <strong>串联焊接在杜邦线上</strong>, 不是焊到PCB上:</p>
<ol style="margin-left:20px;line-height:2.2;">
  <li>取杜邦线, 一端接 <strong>ESP32 3.3V 引脚</strong></li>
  <li>在杜邦线中间剥开绝缘皮, 串联焊入 4.7kΩ 电阻</li>
  <li>电阻另一端分别接到 GPIO20(SDA) 和 GPIO13(SCL) 的杜邦线上</li>
  <li>焊接点用 <strong>热缩管</strong> 绝缘</li>
</ol>
<p style="color:#f59e0b;">⚠ 如果触摸屏完全无反应, 首先检查这两颗上拉电阻是否焊接正确!</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>6.3 GPIO21 电机 START 下拉电阻 (安全停机)</h3>
<div class="callout danger">
  <strong>为什么需要下拉?</strong>
  ESP32-S3 上电时 GPIO 默认为浮空输入状态, 电平不确定。如果 GPIO21 浮空, 电机可能在 MCU 还没初始化时就意外启动! 下拉电阻确保 GPIO21 默认低电平 → 电机安全停机。
</div>
<div class="wire-box">
<pre style="font-family:Consolas,monospace;font-size:.85em;line-height:1.6;">
    ESP32 GPIO21 (开漏/推挽输出)
       │
       ├─────────── Motor START (黄线)
       │
       R = 4.7kΩ ±5% (下拉)
       │
      GND

    原理: 上电时 GPIO21 浮空 → 4.7kΩ拉至 GND → 低电平 → 电机不转
          MCU 初始化后拉高 GPIO21 → 电流流过 4.7kΩ (仅 ~0.7mA) → 电机启动
</pre>
</div>
<p><strong>焊接方式 (与上拉相同):</strong></p>
<ol style="margin-left:20px;line-height:2.2;">
  <li>取杜邦线, 一端接 GPIO21 杜邦线, 另一端接 GND</li>
  <li>在杜邦线中间剥开绝缘皮, <strong>串联焊入 4.7kΩ 电阻</strong></li>
  <li>焊接点用 <strong>热缩管</strong> 绝缘</li>
  <li>⚠ 注意: 电阻是并接在 GPIO21 和 GND 之间, 不是串在信号通路中!</li>
</ol>
<div class="callout info">
  <strong>为什么不直接用内部下拉?</strong>
  ESP32 内部下拉约 45kΩ, 阻值太大。上电瞬间 GPIO 处于高阻态 (~µs级), 电机驱动板可能误触发。外部 4.7kΩ 强下拉确保在任何情况下 GPIO21 都是确定的低电平。
</div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<h2>七、音频电路 (RC滤波 + PAM8302 功放)</h2>

<div class="card">
<h3>7.1 RC 低通滤波器</h3>
<p>ESP32 LEDC 输出的 PWM 方波包含高频谐波, 直接送入功放会产生刺耳噪声。RC 低通滤波器滤除高频成分, 保留音频信号:</p>
<div class="wire-box">
<pre style="font-family:Consolas,monospace;font-size:.85em;line-height:1.6;">
    GPIO48 (LEDC PWM 44.1kHz)
       │
       R (100Ω)
       │
       ├────── PAM8302 IN+
       │
       C (10nF)
       │
      GND

    截止频率 fc = 1 / (2π × R × C)
                = 1 / (2π × 100 × 10×10⁻⁹)
                ≈ 159 kHz
</pre>
</div>
<p>44.1kHz 音频采样频率远低于 159kHz 截止频率, 因此音频信号几乎无衰减通过。高频PWM载波 (MHz级) 被大幅衰减。</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>7.2 PAM8302 引脚说明</h3>
<div class="tbl-wrap">
<table>
<thead><tr><th>引脚</th><th>连接</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>VCC</td><td>CH3 +5V</td><td>2.5W输出时电流约500mA</td></tr>
<tr><td>GND</td><td>共地</td><td>—</td></tr>
<tr><td>IN+</td><td>RC滤波输出</td><td>音频信号正输入</td></tr>
<tr><td>IN-</td><td>GND</td><td>音频信号负输入 (单端模式接地)</td></tr>
<tr><td>SD</td><td>3.3V</td><td>Shutdown (低电平关断, 高电平使能)</td></tr>
<tr><td>OUT+</td><td>喇叭 +</td><td>差分输出正</td></tr>
<tr><td>OUT-</td><td>喇叭 -</td><td>差分输出负</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<h2>八、WS2812 智能 RGB LED 状态灯</h2>

<div class="card">
<h3>8.1 硬件连接</h3>
<div class="tbl-wrap">
<table>
<thead><tr><th>WS2812 引脚</th><th>连接</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>VDD</td><td>CH3 +5V</td><td>WS2812 需5V供电 (3.3V也可亮但颜色偏暗)</td></tr>
<tr><td>GND</td><td>共地</td><td>—</td></tr>
<tr><td>DIN</td><td>GPIO38</td><td>RMT外设驱动, 3.3V逻辑兼容</td></tr>
<tr><td>DOUT</td><td>NC (悬空)</td><td>级联下一颗灯珠用, 本项目仅1颗</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>8.2 状态灯颜色定义</h3>
<div class="tbl-wrap">
<table>
<thead><tr><th>设备状态</th><th>颜色</th><th>效果</th><th>R</th><th>G</th><th>B</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr style="background:#fef2f2;"><td>传感器报警 (TVOC/CO2/CH2O超标)</td><td style="color:#dc2626;font-weight:700;">红色</td><td>闪烁 (500ms)</td><td>255</td><td>0</td><td>0</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#fff7ed;"><td>关机中</td><td style="color:#ea580c;font-weight:700;">橙色</td><td>常亮→渐灭</td><td>255</td><td>80</td><td>0</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#fff7ed;"><td>WiFi连接失败</td><td style="color:#f97316;font-weight:700;">橙红</td><td>慢闪 (1s)</td><td>255</td><td>60</td><td>0</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#eff6ff;"><td>WiFi连接中</td><td style="color:#2563eb;font-weight:700;">蓝色</td><td>闪烁 (300ms)</td><td>0</td><td>80</td><td>255</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f0fdf4;"><td>正常运行</td><td style="color:#16a34a;font-weight:700;">绿色</td><td>常亮 (可自定义)</td><td>0</td><td>255</td><td>0</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p>优先级: <strong>报警 > 关机 > WiFi故障 > WiFi连接中 > 正常运行</strong>。高优先级状态会覆盖低优先级显示。</p>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<h2>九、DS18B20 温度测量电路</h2>

<div class="card">
<h3>9.1 分压电路原理</h3>
<div class="wire-box">
<pre style="font-family:Consolas,monospace;font-size:.85em;line-height:1.6;">
    CH4 3.3V (独立参考电压)
       │
       R_ref = 1kΩ ±0.1% 精密金属膜电阻
       │
       ├──── GPIO8 (ADC1_CH7, 12-bit SAR)
       │
       DS18B20 (数字 1-Wire, 12-bit, 出厂已校准)
       │
      GND

    温度 = raw / 16.0 (°C)  ·  raw = scratchpad[1:0] (小端序补码)

    0°C:   V_adc = 3.3 × 1000 / 2000 = 1.650V
    25°C:  V_adc = 3.3 × 1097 / 2097 ≈ 1.727V
    100°C: V_adc = 3.3 × 1385 / 2385 ≈ 1.916V
</pre>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>9.2 精度考量</h3>
<ul style="margin-left:20px;line-height:2;">
  <li><strong>R_ref 精度:</strong> 使用 ±0.1% 精密电阻 (而非普通 ±5% 碳膜)。1%误差 → 约0.4°C误差</li>
  <li><strong>ADC 分辨率:</strong> ESP32-S3 12-bit SAR ADC, 3.3V参考 → 0.81mV/LSB。在25°C附近每LSB约对应0.12°C</li>
  <li><strong>供电:</strong> 可使用 ESP32 板载 3.3V 供电, DS18B20 工作电流仅 1mA
  <li><strong>两线制局限:</strong> 导线电阻串入测量回路, 长线时建议改用三线制或四线制</li>
</ul>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<h2>十、上电验证清单</h2>

<div class="card hl" style="border-color:#10b981;">
<h3 style="color:#10b981;">逐项检查 — 全部通过后再通电</h3>
<ul class="chk">
  <li><strong>极性检查:</strong> 电解电容长脚→正, 短脚→负</li>
  <li><strong>极性检查:</strong> 电机红→12V+, 黑→GND</li>
  <li><strong>电源隔离:</strong> DS18B20 VDD → 3.3V · DQ → GPIO8 (4.7kΩ上拉)
  <li><strong>GND共地:</strong> 所有模块GND连通 (万用表蜂鸣档)</li>
  <li><strong>上拉电阻:</strong> SDA/SCL 各有4.7kΩ→3.3V</li>
  <li><strong>下拉电阻:</strong> GPIO21 有4.7kΩ→GND (安全停机)</li>
  <li><strong>RC滤波:</strong> 100Ω+10nF 焊接在GPIO48和PAM8302之间</li>
  <li><strong>DS18B20 1-Wire:</strong> DQ接GPIO8, 4.7kΩ上拉至3.3V (必须焊!)</li>
  <li><strong>退耦电容:</strong> ESP32/电机/Y01/LCD 各并联100nF</li>
  <li><strong>电机补偿:</strong> 470µF电解并联在12V和GND之间</li>
  <li><strong>UART交叉:</strong> Y01 TX→ESP32 RX(GPIO9), Y01 RX←ESP32 TX(GPIO41)</li>
  <li><strong>无短路:</strong> 万用表测各电源轨对GND无短路</li>
  <li><strong>裸线绝缘:</strong> 所有焊点已套热缩管或包电工胶带</li>
  <li><strong>AC安全:</strong> 船型开关确认在OFF位</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>通电顺序</h3>
<div class="steps">
<div class="step"><div class="num">1</div><div class="info"><strong>断开所有负载, 空载测电源</strong><span>先不接ESP32等模块, 万用表测DPC3512四路输出电压: CH1≈5.0V, CH2≈12.0V, CH3≈5.0V, CH4≈3.3V</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">2</div><div class="info"><strong>断电, 接上所有负载</strong><span>按接线图接好所有模块, 再次确认极性</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">3</div><div class="info"><strong>通电, 观察状态灯</strong><span>ESP32启动后LCD应显示Logo, WS2812状态灯按WiFi状态显示颜色</span></div></div>
<div class="step"><div class="num">4</div><div class="info"><strong>功能验证</strong><span>触摸屏操作正常 → WiFi连接正常 → 传感器数据更新 → 电机控制正常 → 音频播放正常</span></div></div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<h2>十一、故障排查</h2>

<div class="card">
<h3>11.1 常见问题速查</h3>
<div class="tbl-wrap">
<table>
<thead><tr><th>现象</th><th>可能原因</th><th>排查方法</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>

<tr>
  <td>LCD白屏/不显示</td>
  <td>背光PWM未输出 · 数据线接错 · FPC排线松动</td>
  <td>万用表测GPIO19电压 (背光0-100%对应0-3.3V) · 检查D0-D7线序 · 重插FPC排线</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>触摸无反应</td>
  <td>I2C上拉电阻缺失 · SDA/SCL接反 · 地址错误</td>
  <td>示波器看SDA/SCL波形 · 检查4.7kΩ上拉 · I2C扫描地址0x38</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>电机不转</td>
  <td>GPIO21未拉高 · 12V供电异常 · 电机线接反</td>
  <td>串口发启动命令 · 测CH2 12V输出 · 用万用表测电机红黑线电压</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>电机转速不稳</td>
  <td>470µF电容未接/虚焊 · PWM频率不对</td>
  <td>检查电解电容焊点 · 确认LEDC设为25kHz</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>Y01无数据</td>
  <td>TX/RX未交叉 · 波特率不对 · 5V供电异常</td>
  <td>确认Y01 TX→ESP32 RX(GPIO9) · 9600bps · 测CH3 5V</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>温度读数偏差大</td>
  <td>分压电阻精度不够 · 导线电阻影响</td>
  <td>换±0.1%精密电阻 · 缩短DS18B20引线 (1-Wire 飞线≤30cm)</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>喇叭无声/杂音</td>
  <td>RC滤波未焊 · PAM8302 SD未拉高 · 功放供电不足</td>
  <td>检查100Ω+10nF焊接 · SD脚测3.3V · CH3电流足够</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>WS2812不亮</td>
  <td>DIN信号线断 · 5V供电缺失 · RMT配置错误</td>
  <td>GPIO38到DIN通断 · CH3 5V到WS2812 VDD · 检查GRB字节顺序</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td>WiFi连不上</td>
  <td>天线未插 · 信号弱 · 路由器兼容性</td>
  <td>确认天线拧紧 · 靠近路由器测试 · 尝试2.4GHz频段</td>
</tr>

</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h3>11.2 关键测试点电压</h3>
<div class="tbl-wrap">
<table>
<thead><tr><th>测试点</th><th>正常电压</th><th>万用表档位</th></tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr><td>DPC3512 CH1 (+5V)</td><td>4.95-5.05V</td><td>DC 20V</td></tr>
<tr><td>DPC3512 CH2 (+12V)</td><td>11.8-12.2V</td><td>DC 20V</td></tr>
<tr><td>DPC3512 CH3 (+5V)</td><td>4.95-5.05V</td><td>DC 20V</td></tr>
<tr><td>DPC3512 CH4 (+3.3V)</td><td>3.25-3.35V</td><td>DC 20V</td></tr>
<tr><td>ESP32 3.3V 引脚</td><td>3.25-3.35V</td><td>DC 20V</td></tr>
<tr><td>GPIO19 (LCD背光 100%)</td><td>≈3.3V</td><td>DC 20V</td></tr>
<tr><td>GPIO21 (电机启动)</td><td>≈3.3V</td><td>DC 20V</td></tr>
<tr><td>GPIO8 (DS18B20 DQ, 空闲)</td><td>≈3.3V (上拉) / 通信时脉冲0V</td><td>DC 20V</td></tr>
<tr><td>SDA/SCL (空闲)</td><td>≈3.3V</td><td>DC 20V</td></tr>
<tr><td>PAM8302 SD (使能)</td><td>≈3.3V</td><td>DC 20V</td></tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
<h2>十二、10×10cm 洞洞板布局</h2>

<div class="card">
<h3>12.1 交互式 PCB 布局查看器</h3>
<p>
  100×100mm · 2.54mm间距 · DPC3512供电 · LCD排针对插 · WS2812板载
  <b>点击导线→高亮网络</b> | 滚轮缩放 | 拖拽平移 | 图层切换显隐
</p>

<style>
#pv{font-family:'Segoe UI',system-ui,sans-serif;background:#0a1f12;border:1px solid #374151;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;}
#pv .tb{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:5px 10px;background:#0d2818;border-bottom:1px solid #1e3a2a;flex-wrap:wrap;}
#pv .tb label{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:3px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:3px;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;color:#ccc;background:#132a1c;border:1px solid #2d5a3d;user-select:none;}
#pv .tb label:hover{background:#1a3a25;}
#pv .tb label input{accent-color:#4a9a5f;}
#pv .tb button{padding:3px 10px;border-radius:3px;font-size:11px;cursor:pointer;color:#ccc;background:#132a1c;border:1px solid #2d5a3d;}
#pv .tb button:hover{background:#1a3a25;}
#pv .tb .sp{width:1px;height:16px;background:#2d5a3d;}
#pv .tip{padding:3px 10px;font-size:11px;color:#60d080;background:#0d2818;border-top:1px solid #1e3a2a;min-height:18px;}
#pv .tip.on{background:#0a3018;color:#80f0a0;font-weight:600;}
#pv .wrap{overflow:auto;max-height:800px;background:#061208;}
#pv svg{display:block;min-width:1100px;width:100%;transform-origin:top left;cursor:grab;}
#pv svg .nt{transition:opacity 0.35s;cursor:pointer;}
#pv svg .nt path,#pv svg .nt line{stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
#pv svg.dim .nt{opacity:0.10;}
#pv svg.dim .nt.hi{opacity:1;}
.nt.hi path,.nt.hi line{filter:drop-shadow(0 0 6px currentColor);stroke-width:6!important;}
.nt.hi circle.pd{filter:drop-shadow(0 0 4px currentColor);}
</style>

<div id="pv">
<div class="tb">
  <span style="color:#9ca3af;font-size:11px;">图层:</span>
  <label><input type="checkbox" checked data-ly="traces" onchange="tL(this)">走线</label>
  <label><input type="checkbox" checked data-ly="pads" onchange="tL(this)">焊盘</label>
  <label><input type="checkbox" checked data-ly="silkscreen" onchange="tL(this)">丝印</label>
  <label><input type="checkbox" checked data-ly="labels" onchange="tL(this)">标注</label>
  <label><input type="checkbox" checked data-ly="comps" onchange="tL(this)">元件</label>
  <span class="sp"></span>
  <button onclick="rH()">清除高亮</button>
  <button onclick="z2('+')">＋</button>
  <button onclick="z2('-')">－</button>
  <button onclick="zr2()">1:1</button>
</div>
<div class="wrap" id="pvWrap">
<svg id="pvSvg" viewBox="0 0 1160 1100">

<defs>
  <pattern id="gh" width="25.4" height="25.4" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
    <circle cx="12.7" cy="12.7" r="2" fill="#143620" stroke="#22663a" stroke-width="0.3"/>
  </pattern>
  <marker id="m12" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#ef7676"/></marker>
  <marker id="m5"  mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#f0a060"/></marker>
  <marker id="m33" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#6090e0"/></marker>
  <marker id="mG"  mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#909090"/></marker>
  <marker id="mCLK" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#40c8d8"/></marker>
  <marker id="mC5" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#2098a8"/></marker>
  <marker id="mFG" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#30b898"/></marker>
  <marker id="mDQ" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#b090f0"/></marker>
  <marker id="mRX" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#c080e8"/></marker>
  <marker id="mTX" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#e070d0"/></marker>
  <marker id="mAU" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#f06070"/></marker>
  <marker id="mSH" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#e85088"/></marker>
  <marker id="mSD" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#d0a050"/></marker>
  <marker id="mSC" mkWidth="7" mkHeight="6" refX="6" refY="3" orient="auto"><polygon points="0 0,7 3,0 6" fill="#c0a030"/></marker>
</defs>

<!-- ══ BOARD ══ -->
<g data-ly="board">
  <rect x="50" y="50" width="1000" height="1000" fill="#1a5632" stroke="#0f3d20" stroke-width="3" rx="1"/>
  <rect x="50" y="50" width="1000" height="1000" fill="url(#gh)"/>
  <rect x="47" y="47" width="1006" height="1006" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.3)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="18,8" rx="2"/>
  <text x="550" y="1068" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.35)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" font-family="monospace">100×100mm · 2.54mm间距 · 39×39孔</text>
</g>

<!-- ══ POWER TERMINALS (top-left) ══ -->
<g data-ly="silkscreen">
  <rect x="70" y="58" width="100" height="50" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.55)" stroke-width="1" rx="2"/>
  <text x="120" y="78" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.75)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-family="monospace">12V IN</text>
  <rect x="190" y="58" width="100" height="50" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.55)" stroke-width="1" rx="2"/>
  <text x="240" y="78" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.75)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-family="monospace">5V IN</text>
  <rect x="310" y="58" width="100" height="50" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.55)" stroke-width="1" rx="2"/>
  <text x="360" y="78" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.75)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-family="monospace">3V3 IN</text>
  <rect x="430" y="58" width="100" height="50" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.55)" stroke-width="1" rx="2"/>
  <text x="480" y="78" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.75)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-family="monospace">GND IN</text>
</g>

<!-- Terminal pads -->
<g data-ly="pads">
  <circle cx="95" cy="98" r="4" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="12V"/>
  <circle cx="145" cy="98" r="4" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="12V"/>
  <circle cx="215" cy="98" r="4" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="5V"/>
  <circle cx="265" cy="98" r="4" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="5V"/>
  <circle cx="335" cy="98" r="4" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="3V3"/>
  <circle cx="385" cy="98" r="4" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="3V3"/>
  <circle cx="455" cy="98" r="4" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="GND"/>
  <circle cx="505" cy="98" r="4" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="GND"/>
</g>

<!-- ══ POWER BUS BARS (3V3+GND extended to x=100 for left-side access) ══ -->
<g class="nt" data-net="12V" data-ly="traces"><line x1="560" y1="140" x2="1060" y2="140" stroke="#ef7676" stroke-width="5"/></g>
<g class="nt" data-net="5V" data-ly="traces"><line x1="100" y1="170" x2="1060" y2="170" stroke="#f0a060" stroke-width="5"/></g>
<g class="nt" data-net="3V3" data-ly="traces"><line x1="100" y1="200" x2="1060" y2="200" stroke="#6090e0" stroke-width="5"/></g>
<g class="nt" data-net="GND" data-ly="traces"><line x1="100" y1="230" x2="1060" y2="230" stroke="#909090" stroke-width="5"/></g>

<!-- Bus labels -->
<g data-ly="labels" font-size="10" font-weight="700">
  <text x="1065" y="144" fill="#ef7676">12V</text>
  <text x="1065" y="174" fill="#f0a060">5V</text>
  <text x="1065" y="204" fill="#6090e0">3V3</text>
  <text x="1065" y="234" fill="#909090">GND</text>
</g>

<!-- Terminal→bus connections -->
<g class="nt" data-net="12V" data-ly="traces"><path d="M145 98 L560 140" stroke="#ef7676" stroke-width="3.5" fill="none"/></g>
<g class="nt" data-net="5V" data-ly="traces"><path d="M265 98 L265 170" stroke="#f0a060" stroke-width="3.5" fill="none"/></g>
<g class="nt" data-net="3V3" data-ly="traces"><path d="M385 98 L385 200" stroke="#6090e0" stroke-width="3.5" fill="none"/></g>
<g class="nt" data-net="GND" data-ly="traces"><path d="M505 98 L505 230" stroke="#909090" stroke-width="3.5" fill="none"/></g>

<!-- 470µF: 12V↔GND at bus -->
<g class="nt" data-net="12V" data-ly="pads"><circle cx="580" cy="140" r="5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7"/></g>
<g class="nt" data-net="GND" data-ly="pads"><circle cx="580" cy="230" r="5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7"/></g>
<g data-ly="comps">
  <rect x="568" y="137" width="24" height="86" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.5)" stroke-width="1" rx="3"/>
  <text x="580" y="165" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.55)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9">470µF</text>
  <text x="580" y="178" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.35)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7">25V</text>
  <text x="580" y="153" fill="#ef7676" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8">+</text>
  <text x="580" y="215" fill="#909090" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8">−</text>
</g>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- ESP32-S3 DevKitC: x=100→530, left pins x=115, right pins x=530 -->
<!-- Labels INSIDE silkscreen to free left side for routing -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<g data-ly="silkscreen">
  <rect x="100" y="260" width="430" height="280" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.65)" stroke-width="1.2" rx="3"/>
  <text x="315" y="285" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.85)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" font-weight="700" font-family="monospace">ESP32-S3-DevKitC</text>
  <text x="315" y="302" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9">2×20P排母 · WS2812板载GP38</text>
</g>

<!-- LEFT pins x=115, spacing=25 -->
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="115" cy="315" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="GND"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="115" cy="340" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="3V3"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="115" cy="365" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7"/></g><!--EN-->
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="115" cy="390" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="DQ"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="115" cy="415" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="UART_RX"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="115" cy="440" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="SCL"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="115" cy="465" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7"/></g><!--GP19-->
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="115" cy="490" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="SDA"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="115" cy="515" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#ef4444" stroke-width="0.8" stroke-dasharray="2,1"/></g><!--GP21 NC-->

<!-- LEFT pin labels INSIDE silkscreen (x=123, anchor=start) -->
<g data-ly="labels" font-size="9" font-family="monospace">
  <text x="123" y="320" fill="#909090" font-weight="700">GND</text>
  <text x="123" y="345" fill="#6090e0" font-weight="700">3V3</text>
  <text x="123" y="370" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)">EN</text>
  <text x="123" y="395" fill="#b090f0" font-weight="700">GP8</text>
  <text x="123" y="420" fill="#c080e8" font-weight="700">GP9</text>
  <text x="123" y="445" fill="#c0a030" font-weight="700">GP13</text>
  <text x="123" y="470" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)">GP19</text>
  <text x="123" y="495" fill="#d0a050" font-weight="700">GP20</text>
  <text x="123" y="520" fill="#ef4444" font-weight="700">GP21</text>
</g>

<!-- RIGHT pins x=530 -->
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="530" cy="315" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="UART_TX"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="530" cy="340" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7"/></g><!--GP42-->
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="530" cy="365" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7"/></g><!--GP46-->
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="530" cy="390" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="SHDN"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="530" cy="415" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="AUDIO"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="530" cy="440" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7"/></g><!--GP38板载-->
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="530" cy="465" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="CLK"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="530" cy="490" r="4.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.7" class="pd" data-net="FG"/></g>

<!-- RIGHT pin labels (to right of pads, inside silkscreen) -->
<g data-ly="labels" font-size="9" font-family="monospace">
  <text x="522" y="320" fill="#e070d0" text-anchor="end" font-weight="700">GP41</text>
  <text x="522" y="345" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)" text-anchor="end">GP42</text>
  <text x="522" y="370" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)" text-anchor="end">GP46</text>
  <text x="522" y="395" fill="#e85088" text-anchor="end" font-weight="700">GP47</text>
  <text x="522" y="420" fill="#f06070" text-anchor="end" font-weight="700">GP48</text>
  <text x="522" y="445" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.35)" text-anchor="end">GP38</text>
  <text x="522" y="470" fill="#40c8d8" text-anchor="end" font-weight="700">GP39</text>
  <text x="522" y="495" fill="#30b898" text-anchor="end" font-weight="700">GP40</text>
</g>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- LEFT SIDE: VERTICAL CHANNELS (x=55→110) -->
<!-- x=58: 3V3 bus  x=70: DQ  x=82: SCL/SDA  x=94: UART_RX  x=106: GND bus -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<!-- GND → bus (left pin 315) -->
<g class="nt" data-net="GND" data-ly="traces"><path d="M115 315 L106 315 L106 230" stroke="#909090" stroke-width="3.5" fill="none"/></g>

<!-- 3V3 → bus (left pin 340) -->
<g class="nt" data-net="3V3" data-ly="traces"><path d="M115 340 L58 340 L58 200" stroke="#6090e0" stroke-width="3.5" fill="none"/></g>

<!-- ══ PULL-UP RESISTORS R1/R2/R3 (between 3V3 bus x=58 and signals) ══ -->

<!-- DQ trace and R3 pull-up (GPIO8 at y=390) -->
<!-- DQ: pin→x=70, then down to DS18B20. R3: x=58→70 at y=402 -->
<g class="nt" data-net="DQ" data-ly="traces">
  <path d="M115 390 L70 390 L70 402" stroke="#b090f0" stroke-width="3" fill="none"/>
</g>
<g data-net="DQ" data-ly="comps">
  <rect x="58" y="398" width="12" height="8" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" stroke-width="0.8" rx="1"/>
  <text x="64" y="410" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7">R3</text>
  <circle cx="58" cy="402" r="2" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.6"/>
  <circle cx="70" cy="402" r="2" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.6"/>
</g>
<g class="nt" data-net="3V3" data-ly="traces"><line x1="58" y1="402" x2="58" y2="340" stroke="#6090e0" stroke-width="2"/></g>
<g data-net="DQ" data-ly="labels">
  <text x="72" y="396" fill="#b090f0" font-size="7" text-anchor="start">R3 4.7k</text>
</g>

<!-- SCL trace and R2 pull-up (GPIO13 at y=440) -->
<g class="nt" data-net="SCL" data-ly="traces">
  <path d="M115 440 L70 440 L70 452" stroke="#c0a030" stroke-width="3" fill="none"/>
</g>
<g data-net="SCL" data-ly="comps">
  <rect x="58" y="448" width="12" height="8" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" stroke-width="0.8" rx="1"/>
  <text x="64" y="460" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7">R2</text>
  <circle cx="58" cy="452" r="2" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.6"/>
  <circle cx="70" cy="452" r="2" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.6"/>
</g>
<g class="nt" data-net="3V3" data-ly="traces"><line x1="58" y1="452" x2="58" y2="402" stroke="#6090e0" stroke-width="2"/></g>
<g data-net="SCL" data-ly="labels">
  <text x="72" y="446" fill="#c0a030" font-size="7" text-anchor="start">R2 4.7k</text>
</g>

<!-- SDA trace and R1 pull-up (GPIO20 at y=490) -->
<g class="nt" data-net="SDA" data-ly="traces">
  <path d="M115 490 L70 490 L70 502" stroke="#d0a050" stroke-width="3" fill="none"/>
</g>
<g data-net="SDA" data-ly="comps">
  <rect x="58" y="498" width="12" height="8" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" stroke-width="0.8" rx="1"/>
  <text x="64" y="510" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7">R1</text>
  <circle cx="58" cy="502" r="2" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.6"/>
  <circle cx="70" cy="502" r="2" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.6"/>
</g>
<g class="nt" data-net="3V3" data-ly="traces"><line x1="58" y1="502" x2="58" y2="452" stroke="#6090e0" stroke-width="2"/></g>
<g data-net="SDA" data-ly="labels">
  <text x="72" y="496" fill="#d0a050" font-size="7" text-anchor="start">R1 4.7k</text>
</g>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- LEVEL SHIFTER: x=600→790, y=300→450 -->
<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<g data-ly="silkscreen">
  <rect x="600" y="300" width="190" height="150" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.6)" stroke-width="1.2" rx="2"/>
  <text x="695" y="320" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.8)" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" font-family="monospace">4ch 电平转换</text>
  <line x1="600" y1="328" x2="790" y2="328" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.2)" stroke-width="0.7"/>
</g>
<!-- LV side pads at x=620, HV side pads at x=770 -->
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="620" cy="350" r="3.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.6" class="pd" data-net="3V3"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="620" cy="380" r="3.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.6" class="pd" data-net="CLK"/></g>
<g data-ly="pads"><circle cx="620" cy="410" r="3.5" fill="#c8a050" stroke="#9a7030" stroke-width="0.6" class="pd" data-net="GND"/></g>
